content.detailedDescription: when i get a certain "feeling" i look outside my window, mostly in the direction of south/southeast, & sometimes i get to see a ufo. as for this time, 1:20 pm on sunday the 14th of december, when i got that "feeling" i looked outside & was successful in achieving visual confirmation. at first i thought it was a blimp but noticed it was very shiny like the sun was reflecting off it but it also seemed to pulsate like a close star or nearby planet. also it did not move. at all. just hung in the sky, exactly southeast. i grabbed my binoculars & stepped out onto my porch. through my binoculars it looked more like a helicopter but not as defined. after a short period of 5 or so minutes it started to look more like a giant star or planet & as soon as i noticed that, the object steadily, not light speed but no jet plane, went straight up & out of my view because it seemed to have faded into the clear blue sky in the direction of southeast.
content.summary: It wasn't a plane nor a star nor a helicopter & it certainly wasn't swamp gas reflecting of mars.

content.detailedDescription: I was heading east and i've been feeling a sensation while looking up at the clear, eery night sky. at 2:23am, there was a blu-ish crystal like object that seemed to 'fall' but travel along(skim) the atmosphere. it lasted for about 4 secs and went completely dark. i felt a sense of waitlessness, silence and adrenoline rush. half a second later another object did the same but was smaller, red-orange, and dim. it was going east but not the same path and was at a higher latitude and shorter longitude and lasted about 3 seconds and then that was it!
content.summary: The first object was larger and brighter. the second 1/2 a sec later, faint red-orange, smaller

content.detailedDescription:
Date; 12/13/14
time of event: 4:41am
weather: 42 - 25 degrees, crisp air, clear skies.
i was in my bed trying to sleep, when i heard what sounded like a fighter jet, it seemed to be flying around for a long period of time.  generally, you could hear the jet as it is approaching, then you could hear the sound fade as it flies by. i got curious as to why i could still hear the jet, it seemed to be hanging around a bit longer then what i would consider normal.  i ran downstairs and out the side door.  i could see the lights on the back of the jet, it seemed to be flying a bit low, as if it were looking for something.  i ran inside and grabbed my iphone6 and began recording in the same direction i previously saw the jet. although, i could not physically see the object, my phone seemed to be able to see it just fine. it was a bright yellow/orange orb.  the orb seemed to fade, then come back bigger and brighter.  it seemed to move close, then far, then disappear, or fade in and out.  every so often the color would change to solid red, or blue.  although, i suspect it was the same object, however, upon reviewing the video on my computer, it seems there may have been a fleet of them.  on my computer it seems there are several twinkling lights, i don't believe they are stars.  at times i could physically see quick flashes of light in various locations in the sky. every so often i had to scan over to my upstairs window as a point of reference.  i would point my camera/phone in the position of n, ne, and scan the skies with it, until i was able to see the object.  it moved fast, one minute it was one place, the next it was elsewhere. the video is a bit long, but i wanted to record as much as i could.  i was so excited i couldn't believe what my phone was recording.  i had to run inside and wake my husband to come see.  its funny how it happened on the date 12/13/14.  i have witnessed other crafts; triangle, saucer, etc.. however, this is my first fireball/orange sphere.
content.summary: I heard military fighter jets above my home, went outside and started recording.  i just aimed my iphone6 randomly at the sky where i knew the jet was located.  i could not physically see the ufo, but was able to capture it on my phone.

content.detailedDescription: I was having a quiet night with my boyfriend and i  got taken away i need to speak to someoneabout this help
content.summary: Got taken away

content.detailedDescription: All happened when our south florida fox news team was giving a report on miami's police killing protests and then they showed the city's landscape while a bright light is moving rapidly across it.
content.summary: Rapidly moving bright dome shaped object

content.detailedDescription: I was near the mall at highway 880 and automall looking up at the sky when i saw an object similar to one i reported perhaps a year or 2 ago. it was chevron shaped, and at first i thought it was translucent like the object i reported before. but this time as i watched, the sharp leading edge of what i thought was a craft of sorts distorted. it was very faint, light barely reflecting and difficult to see. it was dark and when it distorted i realized this was a formation of birds. they became more distorted as the formation wavered then regrouped. i suspect now that what i previously reported to you some time ago was the same as now. the difference back then was that the formation was tight and perhaps due to the height or distance from my vantage point, i did not detect any disruption of the birds. they presensented what looked to me like a sharp leading edge of something like a flying wing or a triangle. they were so far away however that they were barely discernable. hope this clears up my previous report. (i actually saw something similar 40 years ago while at a drive-in theater, the object flew over the top of the movie screen, but i could not determine altitude. it was silent and large, also moving southwest at that time and difficult to see, but it had the same shape a triangle or chevron. i watched as it flew out of sight.) ok hope this is helpful.
content.summary: Chevron shaped object seen flying overhead at zenith southbound

content.detailedDescription: Three star like objects in sky - motionless for 2=3 hours over tahoe ca between 1pm and 3pm until cloud cover obscured view. their relative proximity to one another was static.
content.summary: Three star like objects in sky- motionless for 2=3 hours over tahoe ca.

content.detailedDescription:
I opened my garage side door to have a smoke. it was dark and can see sky only straight up between house and rv. immediately seen this red/orange orb like object fly by. no sound and seemed maybe 75-100ft at most above the house. i yelled for my wife and younger son woke up from watching tv laying on couch. they ran out front door i grabbed camera and ran out behind them. we all stood next to my truck in driveway and filmed it until it flew by out of sight. as we did my wife seen another and another behind that one, a total of five. the first two were about 15-20 seconds apart then a plane rather low but it was a jet flew by with all its lights on as they do normally getting ready for airport several miles away. then seen three more of these orbs coming from where the other two came from once jet was clear. could here/feel the jet pass no sound from these orbs (all were the same in look, no sound, and same height all on the same path as if the were on a track. were standing in the drive way freezing it was lower 50's but were floridians (that chilly) and waited no others came. was very clear and stars were bright in sky. but not as close as these orbs were. we have them on film and were left feeling excided and a little freaked out. in no way can i be the only one that reports this tonight. my wife and son have now fell asleep and i'm going back outside with my camera for a little while longer, i'm still alarmed because these things were close enough to be identified and i seen them clear enough. i don't know what the heck it was.  


i have the video on my sony sureshot camera. i am having a hardtime uploading
content.summary: Five of them total. two a pause then three passed by

content.detailedDescription: We were walking up the drive and daughter said " look mom it's your ancient aliens" referring to the show we watch. i looked up in the sky just above horizon and there were 3 lights red orange and pulsing. they started moving, but made no sound. i grabbed my phone and made a 1 minute video. i do not have software to see if it was 1 object ( big ) or multis. lights started moving from right to left with no sound. the 4th light that comes in at 00:20 is a house. that is normally the only lights in that area of landscape. plus we watched it fly right past us. overhead and soundless.
content.summary: Saw lights in sky where there should be none. then they started moving. no sound

content.detailedDescription:
On 12/12/14, at around 8:30 p.M. myself, wife, and four other friends were sitting in the backyard smoking cigars.  this was at our friend's residence in galt, ca.  i was facing east when i saw a bright red/orange fireball falling from the atmosphere. at first i thought it was possibly a meteor or a falling satellite entering our atmosphere.  i became alarmed because it was close and feared it was going to impact nearby as it was at a low altitude. i alerted my friends and they began watching also. the object came to an abrupt stop north east of our location. it hovered and pulsated an orange and red glow. i estimate it was probably 5 to 10 thousand feet altitude. a commercial jet liner beginning it's landing descent into the sacramento international airport flew directly above the object, so it was hovering lower than commercial aircraft.  the object began ascending in a north east direction at a high rate of speed until it disappeared. i estimate this entire event lasted 5 minutes. my wife and friend video recorded the object with their iphone cameras.  

approximately 20 minutes later the same object reappeared. this time it was lower and came more from the south east. it moved slow and deliberately in a north direction, and began ascending at a high rate of speed until it disappeared. it emitted the same pulsating red/orange glow, and had no sound. the object again was captured on video with iphones. 

within 5 minutes the object appeared again in the sky just east of our location. this time it was low, maybe 500 feet altitude. the object was closer this time and moved very slow, stopping in midair at times and hovering. it emitted the same red/orange glow, but because it was closer i could see what appeared to be a cylinder shaped object inside the glow. after less than 5 minutes the object ascended at a high rate of speed until it disappeared. this too was video taped with iphones.

my friends and i are law enforcement and i would consider ourselves trained observers, and very credible. i have a military background and have been around aircraft of all types. this was not an aircraft i have ever seen, nor did it exhibit any typical characteristics of aircraft. we discussed this event over and over and we cannot come up with a logical explanation. one of our friends who was not at this incident suggested it was the atlas 5 launch. this incident occurred well after the atlas 5 launch, plus we are way out of the flight path of rocket launches from vandenberg. i have witnessed rocket launches before. this was not a rocket!! 

when we try to download our three videos to attach with this report it fails saying it is too large. i will gladly supply your investigators with the videos if they would like them and i have no problem being contacted by your organization.  

thank you.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Myself and six others saw a red/orange glowing object hover above us, fly and change directions, and ascend at a high rate of speed. we saw the object on three different occasions, within a 20 minute period on the same night.

content.detailedDescription:
I was riding my bicycle home from work just after dark. my neighbor said, "hey bro, look up it's a ufo" i noticed him taking video of the object and looked straight up to see a large red undulating glowing form directly overhead. it was moving in complete silence several hundred feet up. it looked larger than a cessna and smaller than a jumbo jet, like a mid size aircraft. it was cruising in a straight line maybe going 60 to 80mph. i could tell from it's speed that it would go beyond the trees soon so i did not reach for my cell phone camera. it appeared like a soft glowing form with a bit of a brighter halo on the edge.
i knew then and there it was not of any known earthly technology from it's complete silence. also it's round shape was not like any aircraft currently produced. 
 
a few days later i saw my neighbor and asked for a copy of the video he took. keep in mind what we both saw was reddish in color. however the video he provided shows a bluish object. so again this being recorded as blue is like no camera aberration i have ever seen. it turns out my neighbor when taking the video actually held a pair of binoculars to his camera lens as a way to magnify it. hence when you see the video a small white spot appears which was probably caused from looking through the multi lens binocular.
content.summary: Soft round glowing shape, dull reddish glow, definitely under some type of silent propulsion

content.detailedDescription: I was shooting a timelapse of the storm that was approaching in simi valley, ca. i got the idea to put the gopro (1st generation) on the roof and switched it's view from southeast to north east a few minutes after setting it to run. i went inside to not be rained on. it wasn't until i looked at the video with a frame by frame mentality after about a week of the occurrence that i noticed an anomaly, i saw nothing with my own eyes. as i was looking at each frame i noticed right after the heavy downfall that there seemed to be (something) darting through the image. once i changed the image look (with adjustments to exposure, contrast etc...) whatever this thing was became more defined. this is a high def camera with no flaws and still works perfectly to date. i don't know what i'm looking at and it has confused everyone i have showed it to. i am putting it out there to try and get some real answers but that continues to be my desire. everything else natural in the frames are visible.... birds, raindrops, etc. what am i looking at here?
content.summary: Hiding in a rainstorm

content.detailedDescription: On this occasion the bright light was glowing in the sky. it was only about 100 ft off the ground and stationery for a min then started rising and stopping. then the light slowly went off and a black object remained for a second before a duller light came on and the object rose into the cloud cover. the weather was clear and sunset was behind me. i have seen this same object over the village before late at night again on a clear cold night about a month before and on this occasion it moved fast dropping into the fields and hovering about 50th off the ground then climbing again. i was about two miles away across the fields with my dog.
content.summary: Second time i have seen this light here. hovering and lowering before ascending

content.detailedDescription: Same as the one reported on dec 9. we had some cloud clearing that evening, and lasted just a while, long enough to see it for a few minutes. i took out my ipad i took a picture and recorded the object. clouded and rain came through and covered it. for just a little bit, i could see its light behind the clouds.
content.summary: Same position as the ufo i reported on dec 9.Had a flat top and relatively flat bottom.

content.detailedDescription: Ive been night watching here in columbia mo.,ive been seeing these orbs flying around the night sky sometimes they look like stars then they move,.The donbt blink and when i look through the binnoculars it looks orb.,just glowing away no wings or nothing,.I see them all the time everynight i go out and spend a few hours looking i will see something,..,if there is anyway mufon u all can get binnoculars that take video i gurantee u will get them on video,..,i see them more than i dont put it that way,..,ive lived by airports lived right next to ohare in chicago so im sued to seeing planes flying through the sky.,,.And when u look through binoculare at a plane u cann see its wings and multiple lights not just one light thats flying.,,.Is there any investagators in or around columbia missouri?.,just watch the stars at night i wish i could video tape them but my phone cant do that that well,.,.So im stuck watching them nightly through my binnoculars.,hopefully one day soon ill beable to get u all some video so u have more evidence,.Thank u very much i really hope the truth comes out soon.,,.There is so much more that flies around.,i cannot believe how many people dont watch,..,i would love for people to come watch what im seeing so they can see to and hopefully believe,.,.I seen multiple objects last night most u couldnt see with out a helping eye binnoculars..I usually see mutiple last night i seen one then few miles i guess over was another same hight just about off the ground flying the same way again no wings just one light,..,..,everyone wants evidence well columbia mo watch the night skies watch for moving stars use binnoculars watch the sky and u will see make sure your a little out of town so u can see better i live a little outside of town so town lights dont bother me much i can see the greatly,.,.Drives me insane i cant take video of them,.,.But there here,.Thats for sure,..,
content.summary: Been seeing alot of them lately

content.detailedDescription: before daylight i placed my gopro camera on my deck to catch a stop motion video of the sunrise. when reviewing the pictures, i noticed the object streaking through the sky. it may be aircraft contrails but i thought a professional may want to look at it.
content.summary: Found pictures of unknown flying object in camera after filming sunrise with stop motion

content.detailedDescription: Last october 2014, i was staring at the full moon when suddenly 3 white orbs in an isosceles-type triangular formation flew in a swift gliding motion and moved towards/passed by me taking a westerly path.  the lights are close to around 100ft or so but no sound was heard as if there was no engine like that of a jet or commercial plane.  it was fast, took only a few seconds to fly across the sky.  it is not like a meteor that leaves a streaking white line in the night sky when it enters the atmosphere.   these 3 bright orbs remained circular in its shape as it traveled and maintained its distance between one another as it moved about.
content.summary: 3 white orbs in triangular formation

content.detailedDescription: I was out side looking at the stars. it was a clear cool night. i was laying on the hood of my car facing the west. what made me look twice is a bright white light traveling northwest to the southwest just above and following the tree line that runs that direction. i thought it was a plane going to our local airport. i looked to see if any more aircraft was in the air and there was none. so i glued my eyes to it. thinking it was a little to low. as soon as i was locked on it. it was like it knew i was watching it. the white light that was traveling southwest now turned strait north got above the power lines over our road that runs east to west, it made a 90 degree turn to our road the bright white light went out. but i could still see it. it had glowing light blue lights on each corner of the craft. it was just above the power lines. i watched in amazement. it flew right above me slowly. i was not worried i was at peace. i was thinking take me if you want me. it was a flat triangle. it was like a liquid carbon fiber it reflected light. no noise, no exhaust, no heat. i watched it fly slowly to the east as it flew until i could not see it any more.
content.summary: Ufo was like nothing i seen before

content.detailedDescription:
Pardon my missusing this form.  brad metzler on the history channel is researching the little known missing high definition tv tapes of the apollo landing.

apparently there were high quality tapes made at the satellite stations which were copied by a crude tv camera for transmission to the tv stations and houston.  this was unknown until a researcher saw a clear polaroid of the screen which was then viewed by a 480 tv camera giving out poor quality video we associate with the event.

brad is searching for the lost tapes which reveal a lot the plausible explainations are they were copied over my nasa in a cost saving move in the 1970's since they were data tapes of 15 minutes in duration, or they were ppoorly indexed and are lost in the national archives.

i suspect they were destroyed or siezed by national security as they were clear tapes covering the black out period and the time mission control was trying to shut up the astronauts when they supposedly viewing ufos there.

the implications are obvious if brad were to find them they would be a smoking gun.  i suspect the originals (several sets for different satellite stations) were destroyed but there is a possibility there were unauthroized copies and brad is trying to find them as antiquities offering a $10,000 reward with the help of a former fbi agent who was in charge of their antiquities unit.

you may be able to work with them or conversely they may get shut up fast if these are found because of the plausible evidence of alien interation at the time.

i just wanted to give you a heads up, the contact information is this is false as i don't want to be visited by the authorities...
content.summary: Heads up brad metzler is looking for original clear apolo lunar tv tapes

content.summary: I think it might be named madusa i heard the name after sighting

content.detailedDescription: I was a front seat passenger coming home from work when i noticed a white light traveling at a high rate of speed just above tree tops.  it was being followed by a helicopter which was traveling at a slower pace but on the exact path of the glowing light.  they were traveling in a north easterly and were soon out of sight.
content.summary: Helicopter following fast moving white light sphere of equal size

content.detailedDescription:
On the 5th of december 2014, whilst travelling south along the m1 motorway i observed a bright green light descending in a straight line downwards.  it seemed to travel from a great height. it descended behind the tree line.  as i drove further the trees moved by the green light was no longer visible, however i noticed a red light at the top of a tower/mast, and realised that the green light was in a perfect 'flightpath' with this tower/mast. 

this area has wind turbines and also an array of transmitters or antennas. 
here is a link to what i found out about the area. http://www.Theguardian.Com/notesandqueries/query/0,5753,-24540,00.Html
content.summary: Green light descended vertically over transmitter array located just off m1 motorway.

content.detailedDescription:
It was a beautiful sunny evening, i was on my way to the la airport to pick my husband up, when out of my right peripheral vision i saw something bright that caught my attention. it was a spaceship! i just automatically started laughing because i just took it for granted that there was a movie being filmed nearby. i started liiking for the cranes and wires holding up, and the wardrobe vans. puzzled, and maneuvering from one frwy to another, i began looking around to see if anyone else was seeing it when i discovered all i cpuld see out of my windshield was air. no road, no more trees, just air. my very next recollection is walking into the airport and it is pitch black at night. it was just fuzzy to me. when i received the message that my husband left for me, i went back to my car, which took me forever to fond, because it was on the roof. i never park on the roof.

i have no idea what ensued during the missing time, but 30 yrrs. later, i awoke with one memory, and i am convinced that this actually happened. as i was being released/let go, i was asked some question as to why my body could not be inseminated (telepathically), i replied, "no, i can't have any more babies. i had surgery." 

i have no idea what these entities looked like, as i have no memory. i do know that i felt no fear at any time. i have been having nosebleeds in one nostril ever since and i have physical marks left on my body. i have been holding this experience inside for so long that i have become obsessed with everything ufo, but it's been difficult not being able to share with anyone.
content.summary: Saw ufo while driving to lax. next thing i know road disappeared and me & my car were floating in sky. i lost 7 hrs. missed picking my husband up.

content.detailedDescription:
I was walking to my car at 730, looked up and saw what looked
like a flying angelfish. at first i thought it was a plane, until i noticed the trail which was orange and flowing behind like the fins on a beta fish or angel fish. the object looked like a plane turned on its side with wings facing north and south but with longer, less drastically angled wings. flying with this trail that fully connected. there was a red light somewhat close to the nose but not quite. it flew in a straight pattern flying north from the southwest for about 6 seconds, by the i had my phone out and was trying to get my camera open when it abruptly turned sideways, shimmered blue and white and disappeared. the orange tail was completely gone. i returned to my house completely amazed by what had happened. i've been googling pictures of planes and objects in the sky and i am 100% positive it wasn't something i've ever seen before, and i'm a pretty huge skeptic. it was enough to get me to find this website and try to figure out what this is!
content.summary: Flying angelfish

content.detailedDescription: Standing outside my balcony in west la i was shocked to see a bright glowing solid cylindrical looking object that was flying so fast it zipped through the skyline in less than 5 seconds. i could only estimate it's speed to be well over 1000 miles per hour when it made a sharp turn up into space and i could no longer see it. i did have my telescope beside me but it was already out of range by the time i had looked back up. the only reason i'm venturing to guess this is a vehicle from outer space is because of the tremendous speed and the movement i saw. did anyone else happen to see anything in los angeles around 7:30 pm on 12/12?
content.summary: Ufo zipped through entire sky line in less than 5 seconds at a pace well over 1000 miles per hour and made a sharp directional change upwards leaving the atmosphere.

content.detailedDescription:
Was cooking when i heard my father yelling about a strange light in the sky. storm had broken earlier so it was relatively clear. the arc of it's trail was immediately noticeable as a massive bow wave type arc of light that originated from a dot of blue/white light high in the sky (maybe about 30k-50k feet up). it traveled in an east by southeast direction. i watched for about a minute before i ran inside for a camera. took me less than 30 seconds to get my camera but by the time i reached the front door (it was closer than the side door where my father was) my father yelled that the light was gone. he told me that it had shut off before coming back on for a few seconds, then it sort of broke up or exploded and was gone.
i know what rocket contrails and meteor arcs look like and this object was flying very straight and the bow wave/trail was too big and too wide to be from a meteor or anything man made. rockets don't leave that kind of bright arc. nor do they have that kind of blue/white color.
my house faces directly south so i knew that it was traveling east, from right to left across my line of sight. excited since it was first ufo i've ever seen first hand and i wish i'd been able to get a picture or two of it as keepsakes.
content.summary: Dot of light with a massive arc/bow wave

content.detailedDescription: i was outside my home smoking a cigarette and i was looking south south-west at the stars and a strange object caught my eye. i yelled for my wife to come out side to see what i was seeing.  my wife and kids came running out and saw the bright yellow/orange light that had a crescent shaped trail heading from west to east. we observed the object for about 20 seconds and then the object disappeared into thin air and then about a second later there was a flash where it had vanished. we stood there with our mouths open not believing what we had just witnessed.
content.summary: Bright light with crescent trail

content.altitude: 500 Feet or Less, Over 500 Feet (no cloudcover)
content.detailedDescription:
New years night 2014,about 8:30pm.My neighbor and i where walking to the corner store. on our way home, while crossing the intersection at pacheco blvd. we noticed a very bright light in the sky to our left. so big and bright and hovering very low in the sky. we could not have mistaken it for anything. it was too close. i immediately tried to take photos with my cellphone and thought they weren't taking when i observed the first craft/object release a second object directly below itself. the second craft/ object was identical to the first except in size. the second was somewhat smaller. both craft/objects hovered for a few minutes. the brightness was more than a bright light, it appeared almost faceted, a vivid beautiful reflective light. not painful to the eye. also not easy to ignore.The light was so bright that we could not determine edges, a shape or occupancy. after a few minutes the second,smaller craft/object vanished. gone. now, for another minute or two we were even more closely watching the first craft/object, and just like the other, it too was suddenly gone. the crafts seemed round or sphere like, they were completely silent. there were no smells or noticeable trails following them. they appeared very low in the night sky, and large. from our view they seemed at least basketball sized.
since this sighting i have felt different about the night sky. i initially thought that my cellphone didn't take the photos. about a week later i checked my images and was pleasantly surprised at what i had captured.
content.summary: New years night 2014 a friend and i saw a hovering "light ball" .

content.detailedDescription:
Heading home from work when i first saw it i was thinking that it was a plane
but it had no sound
content.summary: Ufo

content.detailedDescription: Looked like a rocket going up at a weird angle with a huge arc/trail behind it. it had to have been above 30k feet in the air. the arc/trail it left behind was huge and bright, shaped like a boomerang. went slowly above my house and off to the horizon in the s/w (towards the ocean) direction. right before it disappeared, it almost looked like it exploded leaving a plume of smoke/cloud behind. my guess is a test rocket that went off course? thought it was worthy enough to document it here.
content.summary: Looked like a rocket (red dot) with a huge arc/trail behind it. looked like it was over 30k' in the sky, saw it move slowly across the horizon then exploded with a small cloud behind it. rocket perhaps?
